    dc:description "Fig. 4. Aedeagi of Phaenostoma species. A – P. posticatum (Sharp, 1887) (Costa Rica); B – P. kontax sp. nov. (holotype); C – P. stochasma sp. nov. (holotype; Costa Rica); D – P. stochasma sp. nov. (paratype; Venezuela). Scale bar = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4468175/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

